# The purpose is to generate Bicep function types for every POST action of a resource, removing the historical
# restriction to list* operations and relaxing the requirement that an action must have a response body.

Author: Heng Lu <henglu@microsoft.com>
Date:   Tue Feb 27 13:04:07 2024 +0800

    support all actions

